', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/168726/', '', 'Viloxazine', 'Naltrexone, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 1767369485);
